               width=width,
               height=height,
               tools=tools,
               title=str(station))
    for column, series in df.iteritems():
        series.dropna(inplace=True)
        if not series.empty:
            line = p.line(
                x=series.index,
                y=series.values,
                legend="%s" % titles.get(column, column),
